title: Carnival Eats S01E02 Viva Vienna Contraband Days Festival WEB-DL
description:
Carnival Eats - Season 1, Episode 2




Viva! Vienna! Festival/Contraband Days Festival

This trip, Noah Cappe celebrates Memorial Day weekend at suburban DC's ViVa! Vienna! festival, where the fastest way to his heart is through divine Soul Food. Then, he sets course for the bayou where he uncovers some tasty treasures at the pirate-themed Contraband Days festival in Lake Charles, La.




Original Air Date: 25-Aug-2014
